<br>
Hello, my name's Cobbyl Treehuggyr, and I would like to be a moderator of your bass fishing board. Since I have never bass fished, and don't know anything about bass fishing, I think I would be a valuable asset to the community because I won't be biased as to which is the best lure. Let me know!<br>
